        <briefdescription>
<para>Run a self-test on the driver/device. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The test<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Writes to the Interrupt Enable Register and reads it back for comparison.</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>InstancePtr</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is a pointer to the <ref refid="struct_x_hw_icap" kindref="compound">XHwIcap</ref> instance.</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS if the value read from the register is the same as the value written.</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_FAILURE otherwise</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>None. </para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
